{"tid":497241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩急症室打嚟...","createTime":"2017-12-12T14:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T01:49:13.000Z","uid":148551,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf4fd7d55d5f2fa9515925e7635bf9883705ca7","tid":497241,"uid":148551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"我家姐前幾天因為發燒同埋嘔去咗急症室睇 等左幾個鐘照左X光同埋食咗藥之後冇事<br />\n個醫生檢查X光嘅時候冇話有啲咩特別事<br />\n但係正話啱啱急症室打嚟 又話X光報告出咗<br />\n叫我家姐聽日去 話醫生有野要講<br />\n<br />\n我想問有冇人試過有咁嘅情況出現 係咪有乜嘢事...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924bd1d1ad57160bc716514e7fbdd8607c026ea2","tid":497241,"uid":29540,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"你想醫生係電話同你講？"},{"pid":"7927dc57d23d0b4fc86244b91f685c3d45b5249c","tid":497241,"uid":148551,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你想醫生係電話同你講？</blockquote><br />\n打嚟嗰個唔係醫生 佢唔知咩事 <br />\n不過如果可以即刻知道 都好過依家唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"fa05791b8472f8fc4ce80916daf7e4b70948f76b","tid":497241,"uid":37431,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"咩事都好啦<br />\n<br />\n祈禱啦"},{"pid":"21d69bb68d6f461d42cdc343ebee2c1085d031ad","tid":497241,"uid":120854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:10:05.000Z","msg":"有冇抽血？"},{"pid":"268029f1ab4f8f96c29cbf5405b0ab9227c18988","tid":497241,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"嘔 應該係大左肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a53fbbee4bf4c47caebeeda718e20f828dd0c49","tid":497241,"uid":129378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:10:11.000Z","msg":"用得咁嘅語氣通常都係有事，無事唔會即時叫你去"},{"pid":"8b7518d9bab6134a92671f69e84e908db2144e16","tid":497241,"uid":31536,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":