dabb5ff36141e44b7be488","tid":497241,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>X光唔係即刻出即刻睇咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲係啦菲林年代要曬相要睇報告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n係咯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫你返大堂等2個字就有結果</blockquote><br />\n洗鬼兩分鐘，即影即有<br />\n點解樓主張片會事後有人再開黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec051330be96186dba9bcb9e63102c8db392800","tid":497241,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>X光唔係即刻出即刻睇咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲係啦菲林年代要曬相要睇報告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n係咯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫你返大堂等2個字就有結果</blockquote><br />\n就係嗰日個醫生睇完X光報告話冇事<br />\n但係佢今日再打嚟先 覺得奇怪</blockquote><br />\n醫生睇完 之後有需要會要求x光部岀報告<br />\n所以要d時間先有報告睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec25300e0178ac5f3d29dd3089067b8e30c3a98f","tid":497241,"uid":28351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>X光唔係即刻出即刻睇咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲係啦菲林年代要曬相要睇報告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n係咯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫你返大堂等2個字就有結果</blockquote><br />\n就係嗰日個醫生睇完X光報告話冇事<br />\n但係佢今日再打嚟先 覺得奇怪</blockquote><br />\n急症醫生多數淨係識睇大路野 即係有無穿腸呀 腸脹左咁<br />\n放射科醫生通常會睇到多小小奇怪野 <br />\n所以有時call back你番去都唔出奇<br />\n同埋叫你番去 可能都係俾番張referral 你 再去專科排番三五七年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c4e05c684bed92c4df97a33294f082ecbda72d","tid":497241,